OL,3,CNew tech promised to help millions of
OL,4,Ccancer patients receive faster
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FNew technology is to be rolled out
OL,8,Facross the NHS to help millions of
OL,9,Fcancer patients get a faster
OL,10,Fdiagnosis, the government has said.
OL,12,FThe tool, called Cancer 360, brings
OL,13,Fcancer patients' data into one central
OL,14,Fsystem, so clinicians can prioritise
OL,15,Fthose most in need and see patients
OL,16,Fquicker, the Department for Health and
OL,17,FSocial Care (DHSC) announced.
