OL,4,Ccancer patients receive faster
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FIt moves existing analogue systems to
OL,8,Fa digital one, so staff will not have
OL,9,Fto gather important information about
OL,10,Feach cancer patient from different
OL,11,Fspreadsheets, emails, and records.
OL,13,FDr Vin Diwakar, NHS national clinical
OL,14,Ftransformation director, said: "Every
OL,15,Fcancer patient deserves swift,
OL,16,Feffective care, and our new Cancer 360
OL,17,Fsolution harnesses data to ensure
OL,18,Fexactly that. By giving clinicians a
OL,19,Fcomprehensive view of patient
OL,20,Fpathways, we can identify and address
OL,21,Fdelays immediately.
