OL,7,F"The NHS federated data platform (FDP)
OL,8,Fis already showing its value in
OL,9,Ftransforming cancer care, helping our
OL,10,Fhard-working staff deliver better
OL,11,Foutcomes while reducing administrative
OL,12,Fburden. As Cancer 360 expands to more
OL,13,Fhospitals nationwide, I'm confident
OL,14,Fwe'll see meaningful improvements in
OL,15,Fboth treatment times and patient
OL,16,Fexperience."
