OL,7,FIt is understood that trusts will not
OL,8,Fhave to use the tool, but those not
OL,9,Fmeeting the cancer standard `
OL,10,Fincluding that 85% of cancer patients
OL,11,Fshould have started their treatment
OL,12,Fwithin 62 days of being referred ` may
OL,13,Fbe asked to consider how Cancer 360
OL,14,Fcould help them meet targets.
OL,16,FAs well as helping patients get a
OL,17,Ffaster diagnosis, the DHSC said Cancer
OL,18,F360 will also help cut treatment
OL,19,Fdelays and thus boost survival rates.
