OL,7,FThe technology has been piloted at
OL,8,FRoyal United Hospital Bath, and
OL,9,FChelsea and Westminster Hospital.
OL,11,FIt helped Chelsea and Westminster
OL,12,FHospital meet the faster diagnosis
OL,13,Fstandard, whereby 75% of patients
OL,14,Fshould receive a diagnosis or ruling
OL,15,Fout of cancer within 28 days of
OL,16,Freferral.
