OL,7,FSuraiya Abdi, consultant obstetrician
OL,8,Fand gynaecologist at Chelsea and
OL,9,FWestminster Foundation Trust, said:
OL,10,F"The implementation of Cancer 360 has
OL,11,Fenabled my team to monitor and safely
OL,12,Fcarry our patients through their
OL,13,Fcancer pathway.
OL,15,F"The tool enables us to have in depth
OL,16,Fconversations at our weekly meetings
OL,17,Fregarding a patient's next step as
OL,18,Fwell as allowing us to escalate
OL,19,Fqueries directly to other teams for
OL,20,Ffaster turnaround.
