OL,7,FTechnology Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,8,F"I've seen first-hand the stress and
OL,9,Fheartbreak that cancer causes in my
OL,10,Fown family.
OL,12,F"Dependent on archaic pen-and-paper
OL,13,Fsystems, life-saving diagnostics
OL,14,Fappointments hung on whether a post-it
OL,15,Fnote lost its stick, or a piece of
OL,16,Fpaper went missing. That put lives at
OL,17,Frisk, and with the technology we have
OL,18,Ftoday, there's no reason for any part
OL,19,Fof our healthcare service to run in
OL,20,Fsuch a way.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
