OL,7,F"Simply by keeping accurate records,
OL,8,Fthe technology we are putting to work
OL,9,Ftoday will cut waiting times and save
OL,10,Flives, delivering on our plan for
OL,11,Fchange. That way, people can once
OL,12,Fagain trust that their local hospital
OL,13,Fhas the tools it needs to focus on
OL,14,Fwhat matters ` treating their loved
OL,15,Fones and keeping families together for
OL,16,Flonger."
