OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,8,Fthe Government is investing #26
OL,9,Fbillion in the health service, adding:
OL,10,F"It's a long road but we're already
OL,11,Fgetting our NHS back on its feet,
OL,12,Fgiving patients over three million
OL,13,Fmore appointments, hiring 1,500 new
OL,14,FGPs and starting the roll-out of new
OL,15,Ftech that will save lives."
OL,17,FThe DHSC said Cancer 360, to be rolled
OL,18,Fout soon, will benefit millions of
OL,19,Fpatients in the next five to 10 years.
